just_use main.go

# label: ONE_OFF
# role: encodes domain knowledge

The mux and the wireDB() step. Packages that need the DB (auth, views)
get *sql.DB injected here via package-level vars to break the obvious
import cycle.

Entry point: GOPHER_CONFIG → loadConfig → initDB → seedData (demo only) →
buildMux → ListenAndServe. Demo mode auto-sets GOPHER_RESET_DB=1 and
seeds test data; prod never does either. Routes: `/gopher/*` views
(views.RegisterPages), `/admin/*`, `/static/*`, version endpoint. The
old Zulip-compatible messaging API (events/users/DMs/channels) was
ripped 2026-04-21.
